south korean wholes price up 0.2 pct in march south korea 's wholes price index , base 1980 , rose 0.2 pct to 125.1 in march after a 0.2 pct rise in februari but wa 0.6 pct lower than it march 1986 level , the bank of korea said . the march consum price index , same base , rose 0.5 pct to 146.0 after a 0.1 pct gain in februari , for a year-on-year rise of 1.7 pct .